summary: Energy specialist with more than 8 years of sustainable energy project management and research experience. Primarily focused on energy access, renewable energy, energy efficiency, sustainable cooling and heating. A demonstrated history of working in international organizations and with private sector on numerous energy matters. Currently completing a PhD focused on sustainable energy.
